# axe-spider allowlist — known-acceptable incompletes to suppress
#
# Each entry matches by rule ID. Optionally narrow by URL substring
# and/or CSS target selector. Matching incompletes are hidden from
# the report and counted as "Suppressed".
#
# After running a scan, review the incompletes, and add entries here
# for results you've verified are not real issues.

# Example: axe-core can't compute contrast in scroll-snap flex layouts
# - rule: color-contrast
#   url: /
#   reason: Homepage scroll-snap flex cards — axe grid limitation

# Example: suppress all imgNode incompletes from Google Charts SVGs
# - rule: color-contrast
#   url: /usage
#   target: text
#   reason: Google Charts SVG — third-party generated
